body.name: ATX 24Pin 90 Degree Adapter,Motherboard 24Pin Male to 24Pin Female 90 Degree Extension Connection for Mainboard Right Angle Connector for Desktop PC Power Supply
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Tuesday, February 20 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: This ATX 24Pin 90 degree adapter is designed to change the mounting direction of the ATX 24PIN cable. Use this adapter to install the 24PIN power cord from the vertical to the horizontal direction.
Motherboard 24-pin connector is only used for the 24-pin ports to improve the connection between the motherboard and the PSU, which will solve the PSU installation for the limited height chassis
24P female to 24P male adapter use solid pin, stable unbiased needle, strong transmission power, ensure no loss transmission.
Full solder joint, manual welding, thickened EVA insulated cotton to protect solder joint from short circuit.
Right angle ATX 24 pin adapter no longer needs to wind or fold the cable back and forth on the motherboard, solve the problem that the 24pin power cable is too long to insert the ATX 24pin cable.
This mainboard ATX connector prevents problems with accidental damage to motherboard pins through 24pin cables inserted into the motherboard
Connector A: 24 pin male, Connector B: 24 pin female. Installation dimension : 52*18**33MM(LxWxH)
body.description: The ATX 24PIN 90-degree adapter provides a convenient solution for changing the installation direction of the ATX 24-pin cable with a 90-degree L-shaped upward tilt angle adapter. Use this adapter to install the 24PIN power cord from vertical to horizontal.The right-angle ATX 24-pin adapter no longer needs to wrap or fold the cable back and forth on the motherboard. It solves the problem that the 24-pin power cord is too long to be inserted into the ATX 24-pin cable, and prevents accidental damage to the motherboard pins by inserting the 24P cable into the motherboard.Solve the problems of messy wiring inside the chassis, poor wiring at the bottom of the chassis, and vertical plugging of wires to block the hard disk drive.Connector A: 24-pin male, Connector B: 24-pin female.Note: 1. This adapter is only designed for 24-pin ports to improve the connection between the motherboard and PSU. 2. The adapter must be installed step by step to avoid pin short circuit and main board damage. 3. Please unplug the power cord and wait 10 seconds before installing.Installation size: 52 * 18 ** 33MM (LxWxH)Weight: 18gPackage includes: Motherboard ATX 24-pin male to 24-pin female 90 degree connector
